<p><a href="https://itunes.apple.com/us/podcast/airwaves-full-of-bacon/id661984031"><img src="https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5596/14930431416_a172fbac17_o.jpg" width="134" height="50" alt="Basic CMYK"></a> <a href="http://www.stitcher.com/podcast/michael-gebert/airwaves-full-of-bacon-2?refid=stpr"><img src="https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5591/14766809427_8447865091_o.png" width="126" height="50" alt="stitcher-logo-transparent1"></a> <a href="https://twitter.com/skyfullofbacon"><img src="https://farm4.staticflickr.com/3840/14930431476_993ff48576_o.jpg" width="50" height="50" alt="twitter-icon"></a> <a href="https://www.facebook.com/pages/Sky-Full-of-Bacon/69657060403"><img src="https://farm6.staticflickr.com/5589/14930431586_9ce0863fde_o.jpg" width="52" height="50" alt="facebook_icon copy"></a></p>
